TEXT.TITLE: FIRST EASTERN CORP <FEBC> COMPLETES ACQUISITION
TEXT.BODY: First Eastern Corp said it has completed the acquisition of Peoples Bank of Nanticoke, Pa., in an exchange of 11 First Eastern shares for each Peoples share. Peoples has assets of about 24 mln dlrs. Reuter
